products.title: Uniview 3000 Beige Panel Blind
products.metadescription: Uniview 3000 Beige Panel Blind in Cream. Made to measure from £55.68 with FREE UK mainland delivery. This Panel Blind includes 5-year guarantee and child safety features.
products.productdescription: Product ID: DB-PAN0328 Fabric Colour: Beige Material: 30% Polyester, 70% Vinyl on Polyester Headrail: White Aluminium 5 channel track     Control Type: Cord or Wand Energy Saving Rating: ER2 - Medium Energy Saving Value - Effective Thermal Retention Light Filtering: Yes

products.title: Splash Beige
products.metadescription: Buy made to measure Splash Beige Standard Panel Blinds from SoEasy Blinds. Order quality Standard Panel Blinds online today at low prices with fast UK delivery
products.productdescription:
Min Width: 600mm Max Width: 5000mm
 	Min Drop: 450mm Max Drop: 3500mm
 	Composition: Polyester
 	Guarantee: 12 Months
 	Stack: A choice of left, right or split.
 	Controls: Wand control attached to lead panel(s) to manually pull panels across.
 	Headrail: Robust white aluminium track, track depth varies depending on number of panels required.
 	Fixings: Top fix or face fix brackets.
